  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of the study is to compare the quality of dying and death of terminal cancer
      patients from the perspectives of medical staff and main care giver (family). The hypothesis
      is that their view points will be different.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
